description: MSF War Counter suggestions - Merged with Marvel Church data

Tous ont Taunt, ciblez qui vous voulez sauf Ms. Marvel (Classic)

astral.notes: + Ares. Start Scarlet Witch Zombie Basic
+ Guardian (no Elsa Bloodstone), your Daimon Hellstrom needs to have 1+ Daimonds

Stun Big Time with Thing's Ultimate
Stun Big Time with The Thing’s Ultimate

liberty.notes: Check Overpower levels - if higher, fight unpredictable

nightstalker_mephisto.notes: You don't even need Scarlet Witch Zombie
